leadership_approach|process_vision_people_results|graduated|process|vision|people|results|A Process-led leadership sequence|This leadership pattern starts with Process and makes leadership reliable by giving the work structure, sequence, and repeatable standards. Vision strengthens the sequence by linking the work to direction, possibility, and wider meaning, while People and Results add range as the work develops.|The trap is settling the work through Process and Vision before the later signals have shaped the response. People and Results need deliberate attention when the first route starts to crowd out deeper trust and shared confidence or clearer outcomes and next steps.|Follow the sequence from Process to Vision, then bring in People and Results before the first route sets the whole answer.|This is leadership that moves in a clear order, starting with Process before drawing on Vision, People, and Results. It works best when structure is balanced with the later range before the response becomes fixed.|active|leadership_approach::process_vision_people_results::graduated
leadership_approach|process_vision_people_results|balanced|process|vision|people|results|Flexible Process-led leadership|This leadership pattern gives your leadership several usable routes, led first by Process. Vision strengthens it by linking the work to direction, possibility, and wider meaning, while People and Results add range when the priority shifts.|The trap is switching between leadership routes without naming the current priority. Vision, People, and Results need deliberate attention so flexibility becomes a clear choice rather than mixed signals.|Name the current leadership priority, then choose whether the work needs stronger structure and coordination, longer-range direction, deeper trust and shared confidence, or clearer outcomes and next steps.|This is leadership that has access to Process, Vision, People, and Results without relying on one route alone. It works best when the current priority is named clearly enough for others to follow.|active|leadership_approach::process_vision_people_results::balanced
